      <title>由于担心负资产，亨特放弃了对英国购房者的帮助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/hunt-ditched-help-for-uk-homebuyers-on-negative-equity-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣杰里米·亨特曾考虑在上周的预算中为首次购房者提供更多帮助，但由于担心房价可能进一步下跌，因此没有这样做。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/hunt-ditched-help-for-uk-homebuyers-on-negative-equity-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 16:32:46 GMT</pubDate>
